{{primitive|x'y}}

'''Binary search''' performs a binary search on a numeric array <code>x</code> with search element <code>y</code>, assuming <code>x</code> is [[grade|sorted]] in ascending order. It will return the index that is closest to the given search element.

binary search is [[atomicity|right atomic]].

<pre>
  0 2 4 6 8 10'5
 2
   0 2 4 6 8 10'-10 0 4 5 6 20
 -1 0 2 2 3 5
</pre>
